---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About CoursesWyn · Independent Udemy Reviews"
  description="Learn how CoursesWyn researches, verifies, and curates the best Udemy courses for AI, coding, and automation."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-10">
    <header class="space-y-3 text-center">
      <p class="badge inline-flex">Our story</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-white">We write Udemy reviews that still hold up in 2026.</h1>
      <p class="text-white/70">
        CoursesWyn was created to track Udemy programs that deliver real portfolio pieces and job-ready outcomes across prompt engineering,
        RAG, automation, and modern development stacks.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Our review process</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-white/80">
        <li>Audit every syllabus update, instructor announcement, and student testimonial.</li>
        <li>Rank courses by freshness, project depth, community access, and support cadence.</li>
        <li>Publish affiliate disclosures and pricing snapshots for full transparency.</li>
        <li>Cross-reference completion data with portfolio outcomes before recommending.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <article class="card border-white/5 bg-surface/70">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">What we cover</h3>
        <p class="text-white/70">
          Prompt engineering, RAG, generative design, automation stacks, data science, and the highest-impact Udemy development tracks.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card border-white/5 bg-surface/70">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Why affiliate links?</h3>
        <p class="text-white/70">
          Affiliate payouts keep CoursesWyn independent—no sponsored placements, and every pick is vetted by the same rubric.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
